OL,3,CMeet the Archdeacon of Carlisle as
OL,4,CChurch of England faces recruitment
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThe Venerable Ruth Newton has been
OL,8,Fnamed as the Archdeacon of Carlisle as
OL,9,Fshe looks to reduce a large number of
OL,10,Fvacancies within the church.
OL,12,FShe has returned to Cumbria after 17
OL,13,Fyears, having spent the time in
OL,14,FYorkshire, and will look after
OL,15,Fchurches across Carlisle, Brampton,
OL,16,FPenrith and Appleby.
