OL,3,CMeet the Archdeacon of Carlisle as
OL,4,CChurch of England faces recruitment
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThe role is wide and varied for Ruth,
OL,8,Fwho was the youngest church warden in
OL,9,Fthe country when she was aged 26-years-
OL,10,Fold. This was when she worshiped at St
OL,11,FGiles Church in Great Orton.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Ruth said: "I
OL,14,Fwas a church warden. I am not sure I
OL,15,Fwas the best church warden.
OL,17,F"All of those church wardens that I
OL,18,Fwill be having conversations with than
OL,19,Fthey are probably better than I was. I
OL,20,Fwas very young and I worked full time.
