OL,3,CMeet the Archdeacon of Carlisle as
OL,4,CChurch of England faces recruitment
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThe Venerable Ruth Newton explains one
OL,8,Fof her biggest challenges will be
OL,9,Faddressing the recruitment crisis
OL,10,Fwithin the clergy.
OL,12,FShe said: "There are a lot of
OL,13,Fvacancies. People are working on a
OL,14,Fshoestring.
OL,16,F"The pressure on clergy is to work and
OL,17,Fwork and work is really extensive so
OL,18,Fhopefully get a better work life
OL,19,Fbalance than I presently see in some
OL,20,Fareas."
